            "### THE FILE",
            "The intelligence file on Dr. Meera Nair is, at 847 pages, the longest in AKSHAR's archive. Most of it is her own published work. Dr. Bhosle read all 847 pages. She read them over the course of three weeks in 2036, two years before the collapse, and at the end of the third week she wrote one sentence in the margin of the last page: *\"This person already knows what we're trying to prevent.\"*",
