            "**Arjun** is slightly afraid of her in a way he would describe as *\"respectful\"* and she would describe as *\"appropriate.\"*",
            "**Priya** has interviewed her three times for her journal. Meera answered every question precisely and gave nothing away. Priya wrote: *\"She is the most cooperative interviewee I have ever spoken to who has told me absolutely nothing.\"*",
